          "author_name": "Abel Martín",
          "author_url": "",
          "content": {
            "rendered": "<p>I&#8217;ve been years waiting for a write-up like yours. Hopefully, the Docker community starts embracing best practices when it comes to IPv6 networking. Your help pushing for a better understanding of IPv6 in Docker is much appreciated.</p>\n<p>Keep up the good work!</p>\n"
          },
